            <title>[LU-16367] update default ldiskfs features</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16367</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Update the default ldiskfs features used by &lt;tt&gt;mkfs.lustre&lt;/tt&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;enable &lt;tt&gt;large_dir&lt;/tt&gt; on OSTs as well as MDTs&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;clean up handling of other ext4 features that have become a bit messy over time&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;remove obsolete handling of &quot;ext3&quot; filesystems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
